Xtruco Installation Guide

The provided executable was compiled in the following environment:
Linux 2.0.0, X11R6, GNU C 2.7.2. It has also been tested to run under Sun environment.

To rebuild the executable:

Check the Makefile to ensure it matches your system's configuration.
make allclean
make
make clean

If you encounter issues with IPC 'shared memory', comment out the option IPC_OK in the Makefile.

Good luck...

Marcos Martins Duma
